id":255542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:36:22.000Z","msg":"好文好文<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeeaf9504d3803b05fab6ba4676daa9b1737a32f","tid":1458170,"uid":64232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:38:07.000Z","msg":"毛主席說：「我歷來講，知識分子是最無知識的。這是講得透底。」"},{"pid":"bd12177fcbe099fc29ea560ef9a001e9266de142","tid":1458170,"uid":64232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:38:42.000Z","msg":"毛主席說：「知識分子的身體也是不乾淨的，不但思想不乾淨。」"},{"pid":"25c7dfabd3976bfbb9ac2128af054f0df9be956f","tid":1458170,"uid":64232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:40:51.000Z","msg":"毛主席說：「現在這種教育制度，我很懷疑。從小學到大學，一共十六、七年，二十多年看不見稻、梁、菽、麥、黍、稷，看不見工人在怎樣做工，看不見農民怎樣種田，商品怎樣交換，身體搞壞了，真是害死人。」<br />\n<br />\n堅決拆掉所有大學，解放大學生生產力，讓學生回到鄉下耕田"},{"pid":"6d0be0f09119266e9d1e5a3b2d5625dbe78484e9","tid":1458170,"uid":29649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:42:39.000Z","msg":"藍C讀屎片<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff14b4ee5513dbf10d9ccab8b022af89de0ac023","tid":1458170,"uid":64232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:43:56.000Z","msg":"毛主席說：「不要考試，考試幹什麼？一樣不考才好呢！對於考試一概廢除，搞個絕對化。誰考馬、恩、列、斯？誰考林彪同志？誰考我？」<br />\n<br />\n堅定廢除所有考試，考試毒害咱們學生的頭腦，不分是分黑白。"},{"pid":"694439e9e05fee07bc035ed39ee9176718bbe48f","tid":1458170,"uid":45346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:44:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acb1e738ec40561d6cdae7d82f30b368407641c9","tid":1458170,"uid":64232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:45:53.000Z","msg":"毛主席說：「去搞階級鬥爭，那是大學，可以學到很多東西。什麼『北大』『人大』，還是那個大學好！我就是綠林大學的，在那裏學了點東西。"},{"pid":"a93174a1290d19855c62bd2ff37be1cdf5f43dab","tid":1458170,"uid":64232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:49:10.000Z","msg":"毛主席說：「學習馬克思主義，不但要從書本上學，主要地還要通過階級鬥爭、工作實踐和接近工農群眾，才能真正學到。」"},{"pid":"8498513c4cadedb92b51ac8b09e141e449a41642","tid":1458170,"uid":64232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:52:53.000Z","msg":"毛主席說：「考試可以交頭接耳，甚至冒名頂替。冒名頂替的也不過是照人家的抄一遍，我不會，你寫了，我抄一遍，也可以有些心得。可以試點，要搞得活一些，不要搞得太死。」<br />\n<br />\n堅定反對老師處罰作弊的人，作弊的都是走毛主席路線的好同志。"},{"pid":"cd49984d28b159d5d0dd3fcacfb895744a707215","tid":1458170,"uid":27617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:55:43.000Z","msg":"[輸出革命］由今日起，不叫港獨，改叫「廣獨」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1447204\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1447204</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幫手支持廣獨，將革命思想傳入中國！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ehx7Ac4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fehx7Ac4.jpg&h=3f367942&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴打可以用下面條link去印，set左a5 size<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1L7b5VnA5YwhI63YCK-55SGRKkF6GF4jV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1L7b5VnA5YwhI63YCK-55SGRKkF6GF4jV&d=1ZU4T503J%2FBBtE%2F0CauWlcg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=4d4bd2d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1L7b5VnA5YwhI63YCK-55SGRKkF6GF4jV</a>"},{"pid":"88fd6a73ce7935ac6276933dde6b13f230383657","tid":1458170,"uid":64232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd49984d28b159d5d0dd3fcacfb895744a707215","tid":1458170,"uid":27617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:55:43.000Z","msg":"[輸出革命］由今日起，不叫港獨，改叫「廣獨」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1447204\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1447204</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幫手支持廣獨，將革命思想傳入中國！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ehx7Ac4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%